{"sn22.76:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 22.76 ","sn22.76:0.2":"8. Khajjaniyavagga ","sn22.76:0.3":"Arahantasutta ","sn22.76:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn22.76:1.2":"“Rupam, bhikkhave, aniccam. ","sn22.76:1.3":"Yadaniccam tam dukkham; ","sn22.76:1.4":"yam dukkham tadanatta; ","sn22.76:1.5":"yadanatta tam ‘netam mama, nesohamasmi, na meso atta’ti evametam yathabhutam sammappannaya datthabbam. ","sn22.76:1.6":"Vedana … ","sn22.76:1.7":"sanna … ","sn22.76:1.8":"sankhara … ","sn22.76:1.9":"vinnanam aniccam. ","sn22.76:1.10":"Yadaniccam tam dukkham; ","sn22.76:1.11":"yam dukkham tadanatta; ","sn22.76:1.12":"yadanatta tam ‘netam mama, nesohamasmi, na meso atta’ti evametam yathabhutam sammappannaya datthabbam. ","sn22.76:2.1":"Evam passam, bhikkhave, sutava ariyasavako rupasmimpi nibbindati, vedanayapi … sannayapi … sankharesupi … vinnanasmimpi nibbindati. ","sn22.76:2.2":"Nibbindam virajjati; viraga vimuccati. Vimuttasmim vimuttamiti nanam hoti. ","sn22.76:2.3":"‘Khina jati, vusitam brahmacariyam, katam karaniyam, naparam itthattaya’ti pajanati. ","sn22.76:2.4":"Yavata, bhikkhave, sattavasa, yavata bhavaggam, ete agga, ete settha lokasmim yadidam arahanto”ti. ","sn22.76:3.1":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","sn22.76:3.2":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","sn22.76:4.1":"“Sukhino vata arahanto, ","sn22.76:4.2":"tanha tesam na vijjati; ","sn22.76:4.3":"Asmimano samucchinno, ","sn22.76:4.4":"mohajalam padalitam. ","sn22.76:5.1":"Anejam te anuppatta, ","sn22.76:5.2":"cittam tesam anavilam; ","sn22.76:5.3":"Loke anupalitta te, ","sn22.76:5.4":"brahmabhuta anasava. ","sn22.76:6.1":"Pancakkhandhe parinnaya, ","sn22.76:6.2":"satta saddhammagocara; ","sn22.76:6.3":"Pasamsiya sappurisa, ","sn22.76:6.4":"putta buddhassa orasa. ","sn22.76:7.1":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","sn22.76:7.2":"Tisu sikkhasu sikkhita; ","sn22.76:7.3":"Anuvicaranti mahavira, ","sn22.76:7.4":"Pahinabhayabherava. ","sn22.76:8.1":"Dasahangehi sampanna, ","sn22.76:8.2":"mahanaga samahita; ","sn22.76:8.3":"Ete kho settha lokasmim, ","sn22.76:8.4":"tanha tesam na vijjati. ","sn22.76:9.1":"Asekhananamuppannam, ","sn22.76:9.2":"antimoyam samussayo; ","sn22.76:9.3":"Yo saro brahmacariyassa, ","sn22.76:9.4":"tasmim aparapaccaya. ","sn22.76:10.1":"Vidhasu na vikampanti, ","sn22.76:10.2":"vippamutta punabbhava; ","sn22.76:10.3":"Dantabhumimanuppatta, ","sn22.76:10.4":"te loke vijitavino. ","sn22.76:11.1":"Uddham tiriyam apacinam, ","sn22.76:11.2":"nandi tesam na vijjati; ","sn22.76:11.3":"Nadanti te sihanadam, ","sn22.76:11.4":"buddha loke anuttara”ti. ","sn22.76:11.5":"Catuttham. "}